and an intermediate link between the sympathetic trunks and the sympathetic plexuses in the walls of the visceral organs. The development of the prevertebral sympathetic plexuses and of the sympathetic nerves connecting the sympathetic trunks with the vagal sympathetic plexuses probably represents the third stage in the evolution of the sympathetic nervous system.

